						.divider
				// Col-md-12 End
				.row
					.main_feature.text-center
						.col-md-3.col-xs-12.col-sm-6
							.feature_content
								i.fa.fa-laptop
								h5 Application Development
								p.text-justify
									| The basis of any project and the most solid part of our services. Internet applications and cloud based solutions are the future of business. Whether it is an e-commerce website, a cutting-edge startup or even a basic landing page.
						.col-md-3.col-xs-12.col-sm-6
							.feature_content
								i.fa.fa-mobile
								h5 Mobile Development
								p.text-justify
									| Mobile solutions are integral part of our lives. Mobile is always with you, wherever you go, whenever you need it. Open incredible market opprotunities for your business. Make one step forward providing services to customers.
						// Col-md-4 Single_feature End
						.col-md-3.col-xs-12.col-sm-6
							.feature_content
								i.fa.fa-desktop
								h5 IT Consulting
